reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars POWER SPEED DURABLE
reviews.reviewText: This amazing cord came well packaged and I was impressed at the quality when opening. It has a velcro snap on it that keeps the cord manageable when not in use and minimizing excess cord when in use.I have android devices and power banks, car lighter plugs and a power inverter I use in the car that this has worked absolutely perfect on. The dual A, C allows a flexible charging configuration.The cable has a braided design which is both protective and flexible. I feel like it won't fray like some cheaper cables I've purchased and tossed in the trash after only a few months of use.The charging speed is FAST and the data transfer even faster if you use it for that. Color me impressed.The right angle C type plug is especially nice to prevent cable bending and also to set devices in holders without fear of ruining the cable near the plug site. This was what I didn't know if I would like, but I really do! This will be a relief not having wear and tear at the plug in site, which is the reason that power cords usually have to be replaced.Having the option to plug into power with either USB-A or USB-C is fantastic, so it won't matter where I need to charge! Once plugged in, it stays plugged in. The right angle C plug (brilliant design) comes in handy in the wall plug too! This cord works well with power strips and wall plugs with USB options also. The USB cord adapters fit easly and can't be lost because they are affixed tightly to the cord. I've had other cords where they weren't attached to or broke off the cord.I'm really satisfied with my purchase of these cords.

reviews.reviewText: Oh, let me tell you about the braided USB-C charging cable that has taken my charging game to the next level. This cable is like a magician's wand, and I'm about to unveil its enchanting qualities.First of all, the braided design is a game-changer. It's like armor for your cable, and I'm convinced it can withstand anything. I've had charging cables that frayed and gave up the ghost after a few weeks, but not this one. It's like a superhero cape for your device, ready to protect and charge with style.But here's the real charm – the USB-A and USB-C adapters. It's like having a cable that can speak multiple languages. No matter what device you have, this cable can connect, charge, and transfer data effortlessly. It's the ultimate diplomat in the world of charging cables, bringing all your gadgets together in harmony.The speed of this cable is like lightning, and I'm not just talking about its charging capabilities. It transfers data faster than you can say "USB-C." It's like giving your device a turbo boost, making file transfers and backups a breeze.In conclusion, this braided USB-C charging cable with USB-A and USB-C adapters is a true gem. It's tough, versatile, and fast – the holy trinity of charging cables. If you're tired of flimsy, one-trick-pony cables, this one is your knight in shining (braided) armor. It's time to upgrade your charging game, and this cable is the way to do it.
